                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-963" type="given" value="JOHN DAVIES"></interp>JOHN DAVIES WHITE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable I</hi> 46.) I heard the cry of "Stop thief"—I took the prisoner, and found this handkerchief in his side coat pocket—the prosecutor's initials are on it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoners Defence</hi>. I picked it up as I was coming down Holborn, and put it into my pocket two minutes before I heard a cry of "Stop thief," and then I ran foolish-like.</p>
